Print Centrality Measures

Source: R/print.R
print.tna_centralities.Rd

Print Centrality Measures

Usage

# S3 method for class 'tna_centralities'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A centralities object.

...

Ignored.

Value

x (invisibly).

Examples

model <- tna(group_regulation)
cm <- centralities(model)
print(cm)
